originalText.text:
If you work with this agency, be warn! Their agent Sherif, is only in it for the money. He left me homeless and tried to gaslight me. He even told me I should have had a plan B! He lead me on for a whole month that the apartment was mine. He even asked me to leave a deposit for the room to be taken off the market. He waited until the 27 of this month (which was a Friday) to tell me that the other roommate wasn’t approved and because of that I couldn’t move in!! Which makes no sense because it’s separate leases.

He went on to try to force me into a whole different apartment for more money! When I said no, he then was making it really hard for me to get my money back!!

I had to get my father involved at the end and that was when the agency gave my money back within 10 minutes!!!!!

Even though they put me through so much stress and hardship, I did not get any apologies!!!

Also Sherif seems to be in the business of conning people. After this whole thing went down,  someone sent me an article from New York Times and guess what he’s in it!

Please always listen to your intuition!
And don’t let these agents bully you!!!

originalText.text:
What more can I say about this place that hasn't already been said....5 stars without a doubt!!

Mr. Sammy is one of a kind, he truly cares about helping a client not just find a place to call home but also peace of mind!

His office made this stressful process streamlined, quick, and easy. They answered all questions and went above and beyond to accommodate all my requests and concerns.

If you are looking for real estate help of any kind, give them a try! A personal touch to the process is very rare to find these days with all these big box names where you are treated like a number!

Mr. Sammy and this place are from another time.

originalText.text: Great experience with agent Isaac Jaquez. He asked all the right questions, cared to know what was important to me and tailored my options to meet my needs. I told him that I needed a bright apartment, with a bedroom larger than 10x10. The unit he showed me has a 12x12 bedroom, it faces the South facade, with tree large windows in the bedroom, and windows all across the entire unit. The Bathroom have a window, the kitchen have a window. Absolutely sun drenched. Issac really listened to my needs and I absolutely trust I’ll be extremely happy and creative at my new apartment. May I also add the approval process took less than a week, he was responsive to all my text messages and questions, and walked me step by step through the process. Issac made this extremely fast, easy, and I am very grateful. Thank you Issac, I hope to work with you again in the near future.

originalText.text: When I was looking to buy a house there was NO real estate people who want to spend time and effort to help me. Then I found CHASE REAL PROPERTIES. This was the scariest and the best experience because everything started to move so fast that my head started spinning  lol . After Sam helped me buy the house HE also helped me with finding tenants and till today if I have any questions I can call him and he will be there TO HELP. I highly recommend Chase Real Properties for your first home buying experience.
